snippet.title: Cotorro en Mano - Official Launch Trailer (Spanish Audio) | WLG Showcase 2025
snippet.description: A hidden object puzzle game we developed hand in hand with La Cotorrisa, a famous Mexican stand up comedy podcast. You can search in four different areas for up to seven different lists of hidden objects. You can also collect up to 24 objects to decorate the original set of the podcast. With voices by Slobotzky and Ricardo Perez. Cotorro en Mano is available now on the App Store and Google Play.
